OL,3,CMigration must be 'properly
OL,4,Ccontrolled', says Home Secretary
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary has said migration
OL,7,F"must be properly controlled" with
OL,8,Fministers due to lay out sweeping
OL,9,Freforms to the immigration system.
OL,11,FThe skilled visa threshold will be
OL,12,Fincreased to degree-level and
OL,13,Femployers will be told they must train
OL,14,Fworkers in the UK, under plans to be
OL,15,Fpresented to Parliament on Monday.
