OL,3,CMigration must be 'properly
OL,4,Ccontrolled', says Home Secretary
OL,6,FYvette Cooper has blamed a push for
OL,7,Foverseas recruitment for high net
OL,8,Fmigration figures in recent years. The
OL,9,FImmigration White Paper is being
OL,10,Fpresented as part of Government
OL,11,Fefforts to reduce net migration into
OL,12,Fthe UK, with the figure reaching
OL,13,F728,000 in 2024. Net migration is the
OL,14,Fdifference between the number of
OL,15,Fpeople moving to a country and those
OL,16,Femigrating.
