OL,3,CMigration must be 'properly
OL,4,Ccontrolled', says Home Secretary
OL,6,FAccording to the Home Office, there
OL,7,Fwill be tighter restrictions on
OL,8,Frecruitment for jobs with skills
OL,9,Fshortages, businesses will be
OL,10,Fsupported to take on more British
OL,11,Fworkers and employers will be told to
OL,12,Fdevelop plans to train staff in the UK.
OL,14,FIn an attempt to reduce the number of
OL,15,Flow-skilled workers coming to Britain,
OL,16,Fthe skilled visa threshold will be
OL,17,Fincreased to graduate-level.
