OL,3,CMigration must be 'properly
OL,4,Ccontrolled', says Home Secretary
OL,6,FOfficials will also set up a labour
OL,7,Fmarket evidence group to examine which
OL,8,Fsectors are reliant on overseas
OL,9,Fworkers.
OL,11,FMs Cooper said: "We've seen net
OL,12,Fmigration quadruple in the space of
OL,13,Fjust four years, driven especially by
OL,14,Foverseas recruitment.
OL,16,F"We inherited a failed immigration
OL,17,Fsystem where the previous government
OL,18,Freplaced free movement with a free
OL,19,Fmarket experiment.
