OL,3,CMigration must be 'properly
OL,4,Ccontrolled', says Home Secretary
OL,6,F"Employers were given much greater
OL,7,Ffreedom to recruit from abroad while
OL,8,Faction on training fell.
OL,10,F"Overseas recruitment soared at the
OL,11,Fsame time as big increases in the
OL,12,Fnumber of people not working or in
OL,13,Feducation here in the UK."
OL,15,FOfficial figures show net migration
OL,16,Fhas soared since the UK left the EU in
OL,17,FJanuary 2020, reaching a record high
OL,18,Fof 903,000 in the year to June 2023
OL,19,Fbefore falling back slightly to
OL,20,F728,000 in the following year if the
OL,21,Feconomic worsens.
